ен - Стрелок |website=www.abookee.ru |accessdate=2017-07-02 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170728214316/http://www.abookee.ru/index.php/king-stiven/item/188-king-stiven-strelok |archivedate=2017-07-28 |deadurl=no |language=ru }}</ref>。

=== 訴訟 ===

2017年3月，有未知人士對金提起訴訟，要求金給出5億美元以上的賠償金。他稱《黑塔》系列小說的主角羅蘭·德斯欽抄襲自《{{link-en|The Rook (漫畫)|The Rook (comics)|The Rook}}》的主角瑞斯汀·丹恩（{{lang|en|Restin Dane}}）。訴訟者表示，兩者之間的相似之處不僅僅是姓名的首字母縮寫，兩者都有過時空旅行，與怪物戰鬥，且穿著也很相似。此外，訴訟者還指出，兩本書中的「塔」看起來一模一樣。《The Rook》於1977年首度出版，而《黑塔I 最後的槍客》則於1982年出版；金亦曾承認他有讀過《The Rook》。金未對此做任何回應。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.tmz.com/2017/03/28/stephen-king-sued-the-dark-tower-the-rook-infringement/ |title=Stephen King Sued for Ripping Off 'The Dark Tower' Character from a Comic Book |publisher=[[TMZ|TMZ]] |date=2017-03-28 |accessdate=2017-08-22 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170826181742/http://www.tmz.com/2017/03/28/stephen-king-sued-the-dark-tower-the-rook-infringement/ |archivedate=2017-08-26 |deadurl=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-4359096/Stephen-King-s-Dark-Tower-gunslinger-based-Rook.html |title=Wanted: $500 million! Stephen King's Dark Tower gunslinger 'based on character from The Rook comics series' new lawsuit claims |publisher=''[[每日郵報|Daily Mail]]'' |date=2017-03-29 |accessdate=2017-08-22 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170405043830/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-4359096/Stephen-King-s-Dark-Tower-gunslinger-based-Rook.html |archivedate=2017-04-05 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |last=Dick |first=Jeremy |url=https://1428elm.com/2017/03/29/stephen-king-sued-300-million-dark-tower/ |title=Stephen King Being Sued $500 Million Over ‘The Dark Tower’ |publisher=1428 Elm.com |date=2017-03-29 |accessdate=2017-08-22 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170822094748/https://1428elm.com/2017/03/29/stephen-king-sued-300-million-dark-tower/ |archivedate=2017-08-22 |deadurl=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.torontosun.com/2017/03/29/stephen-king-sued-over-the-dark-tower-character |title=Stephen King sued over 'The Dark Tower' character |publisher=''{{link-en|多倫多太陽報|Toronto Sun|Toronto Sun}}'' |date=2017-03-29 |accessdate=2017-08-22 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170822094938/http://www.torontosun.com/2017/03/29/stephen-king-sued-over-the-dark-tower-character |archivedate=2017-08-22 |deadurl=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.themalaymailonline.com/read/article/stephen-king-in-us5m-lawsuit-over-dark-tower-series#RzMUMdxY142M1QFl.97 |title=Stephen King in US$5m lawsuit over ‘Dark Tower’ series |publisher=Themalaymailonline.com |accessdate=2017-08-22 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170830203324/http://www.themalaymailonline.com/read/article/stephen-king-in-us5m-lawsuit-over-dark-tower-series#RzMUMdxY142M1QFl.97 |archivedate=2017-08-30 |deadurl=no }}</ref>外界指出，提起訴訟者在改編電影《[[黑塔_(電影)|黑塔]]》上映前幾個月提起訴訟，其意圖相當明顯：金錢。亦有人指出，兩者之間的相似不見得是侵犯版權，且金早在1969年便開始構思《黑塔》系列和槍客的角色<ref>{{cite web |last=T. Baker |first=Aaron |url=http://stephenkinguniverse.com/stephen-king-dark-tower-lawsuit |title=What They’re Not Telling You About The Dark Tower Lawsuit |publisher=StephenkingUniverse.com |date=2017-03-31 |accessdate=2017-08-22 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170822101341/http://stephenkinguniverse.com/stephen-king-dark-tower-lawsuit |archivedate=2017-08-22 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。

