== 回響與榮譽 ==

截止至2010年，《黑塔》系列小說的正傳七部曲已經在全球40個國家售出超過3000萬冊<ref>{{Cite web|title=Stephen King’s The Dark Tower to Be Adapted into Film Trilogy and TV Series|url=https://www.tvguide.com/news/dark-tower-series-1022747/|accessdate=2020-10-31|author=|date=2010-09-08|last=Stanhope|first=Kate|format=|work=''[[電視指南_(美國雜誌)|TV Guide]]''|publisher=|language=|archive-date=2020-11-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201114054330/https://www.tvguide.com/news/dark-tower-series-1022747/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。書評對《黑塔》系列小說的評價多為正面。《[[華盛頓郵報|華盛頓郵報]]》的比爾·謝漢（{{lang|en|Bill Sheehan}}）稱該系列小說「富含人性」，認為其是「奇幻的史詩」、「真正的大師之作」及「偉大、純然的說故事典範」，並讚譽該系列小說「充滿著出色的橋段……如災難般的遭遇和淒慘的不幸事件等等」<ref name="Sheehan">{{cite news |url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/articles/A27485-2004Sep16.html |title=The Return of the King |publisher=''[[华盛顿邮报|The Washington Post]]'' |date=2004-09-19 |accessdate=2007-08-16 |first=Bill |last=Sheehan |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20171005034704/http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/articles/A27485-2004Sep16.html |archivedate=2017-10-05 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。《[[波士頓環球報|波士頓環球報]]》的艾瑞卡·紐南（{{lang|en|Erica Noonan}}）稱讚了系列小說中的迷人世界，但指出其史詩般的性質對讀者不大友善<ref name="Noonan">{{cite news |url=http://www.boston.com/news/globe/living/articles/2004/01/15/calla_worth_the_read_but_caters_to_tower_fans/ |title='Calla' worth the read, but caters to 'Tower' fans |publisher=''[[波士頓環球報|The Boston Globe]]'' |date=2004-01-15 |accessdate=2007-08-16 |first=Erica |last=Noonan |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170823021203/http://archive.boston.com/news/globe/living/articles/2004/01/15/calla_worth_the_read_but_caters_to_tower_fans/ |archivedate=2017-08-23 |deadurl=no }}{{Subscription required}}</ref>。《[[舊金山紀事報|舊金山紀事報]]》的麥可·貝瑞（{{lang|en|Michael Berry}}）稱該系列小說的前半段為「裝模作樣的大雜燴」，但稱讚了系列小說的結局<ref name="Berry">{{cite news |url=http://www.sfgate.com/cgi-bin/article.cgi?f=/c/a/2004/09/26/RVGR98QA141.DTL |title=Waiting for the end of their worlds |publisher=''[[旧金山纪事报|San Francisco Chronicle]]'' |date=2004-09-26 |accessdate=2007-08-16 |first=Michael |last=Berry |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160312095939/http://www.sfgate.com/books/article/Waiting-for-the-end-of-their-worlds-2722227.php |archivedate=2016-03-12 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。《黑塔》系列小說的粉絲、[[黑塔_(電影)|電影版]]的導演[[尼科萊·阿爾賽|尼科萊·阿爾賽]]認為，史蒂芬·金在故事中結合個人私密和浩瀚史詩的元素是與讀者產生連結的最大原因{{sfn|《世界電影雜誌》2017年8月號||p=72-73}}。差評則有《{{link-en|SF Site|SF Site}}》的馬修·佩克漢姆（{{lang|en|Matthew Peckham}}），他認為系列小說的故事有些問題，如[[血腥之王|血腥之王]]的背景和動機並沒有得到充分解釋，令人失望<ref name="SF Site"/>。

榮譽方面，《[[黑塔IV_巫師與水晶球|黑塔IV 巫師與水晶球]]》、《[[黑塔V_卡拉之狼|黑塔V 卡拉之狼]]》及《[[黑塔VI_蘇珊娜之歌|黑塔VI 蘇珊娜之歌]]》分別於1998年<ref name="WWE-1998">{{cite web |url=http://www.worldswithoutend.com/books_year_index.asp?year=1998 |title=1998 Award Winners & Nominees |work=Worlds Without End |accessdate=2009-07-22 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160411232423/https://www.worldswithoutend.com/books_year_index.asp?year=1998 |archivedate=2016-04-11 |deadurl=no }}</ref>、2004年<ref name="WWE-2004">{{cite web |url=http://www.worldswithoutend.com/books_year_index.asp?year=2004 |title=2004 Award Winners & Nominees |work=Worlds Without End |accessdate=2009-07-22 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160606020139/https://www.worldswithoutend.com/books_year_index.asp?year=2004 |archivedate=2016-06-06 |deadurl=no }}</ref>及2005年<ref name="WWE-2005">{{cite web |url=http://www.worldswithoutend.com/books_year_index.asp?year=2005 |title=2005 Award Winners & Nominees |work=Worlds Without End |accessdate=2009-07-22 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160624054139/https://www.worldswithoutend.com/books_year_index.asp?Year=2005 |archivedate=2016-06-24 |deadurl=no }}</ref>入圍[[軌跡獎|軌跡獎]]的[[軌跡獎最佳奇幻小說|最佳奇幻小說獎]]，但最終分別敗給{{link-en|提姆·鮑爾斯|Tim Powers}}的《{{link-en|地震天氣 (小說)|Earthquake Weather (novel)|地震天氣}}》<ref name="Locus-1998">{{cite web |url=http://www.locusmag.com/SFAwards/Db/Locus1998.html |title=1998 Locus Awards |work=The Locus Index to SF Awards |publisher=''{{link-en|軌跡 (雜誌)|Locus (magazine)|Locus}}'' |accessdate=2015-08-24 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20101008045043/http://www.locusmag.com/SFAwards/Db/Locus1998.html |archivedate=2010-10-08 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>、[[洛伊絲·莫瑪絲特·布約德|洛伊絲·莫瑪絲特·布約德]]的《{{link-en|靈魂護衛|Paladin of Souls}}》<ref name="WWE-2004"/>及[[柴納·米耶維|柴納·米耶維]]的《{{link-en|鋼鐵議會|Iron Council}}》<ref name="WWE-2005"/>。《[[黑塔VII_業之門|黑塔VII 業之門]]》於2005年榮獲{{link-en|英國奇幻獎|British Fantasy Award}}<ref name="WWE-2005"/>。2011年8月，美國[[全国公共广播电台|全国公共广播电台]]（NPR）公布「百大科幻與奇幻小說」的票選結果，《黑塔》系列小說排在第23名<ref>{{Cite web|title=Top 100 Science-Fiction, Fantasy Books|url=https://www.npr.org/2011/08/09/139248590/top-100-science-fiction-fantasy-books|accessdate=2020-10-23|author=|date=|format=|work=NPR.org|publisher=|language=|archive-date=2020-11-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201114054414/https://www.npr.org/2011/08/09/139248590/top-100-science-fiction-fantasy-books|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal|title=NPR's Top 100 Science Fiction and Fantasy Novels|author=|url=https://www.wired.com/2011/08/nprs-top-100-science-fiction-and-fantasy-novels/|last=Wood|first=Roy|date=2011-08-17|journal=Wired|accessdate=2020-10-23|issue=|doi=|others=|year=|volume=|page=|issn=1059-1028|pmid=|archive-date=2020-11-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201114054429/https://www.wired.com/2011/08/nprs-top-100-science-fiction-and-fantasy-novels/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

