=== 漫畫 ===

{{main|黑塔 (漫畫)}}

2005年10月，史蒂芬·金與[[漫威漫畫|漫威漫畫]]簽約，授權出版共七集的限期系列《{{link-en|黑塔系列漫畫：槍客誕生|The Dark Tower: The Gunslinger Born|槍客誕生}}》。該系列的劇情圍繞著年輕時的[[羅蘭·德斯欽|羅蘭·德斯欽]]。{{link-en|羅賓·佛斯|Robin Furth}}負責設計該系列的劇情，{{link-en|彼得·大衛|Peter David}}設計對白，並由{{link-en|傑·李|Jae Lee}}繪製。第一集於2007年2月7日出版，金、大衛、李及漫威的總編輯{{link-en|喬·克薩達|Joe Quesada}}出席[[時報廣場|時代廣場]]推廣該書<ref name="Comic-1">{{cite web |last=David |first=Peter |url=http://peterdavid.malibulist.com/archives/005156.html |title=Peter David discusses the signing on his blog |publisher=Peterdavid.malibulist.com |date=2007-02-07 |accessdate=2010-09-12 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170822134439/http://www.peterdavid.net/archives/005156.html |archivedate=2017-08-22 |deadurl=no }}</ref><ref name="Comic-2">{{cite web |last=Hauman |first=Glenn |url=http://peterdavid.malibulist.com/archives/005169.html |title=Another blog entry of the signing with photos and links to interviews |publisher=Peterdavid.malibulist.com |date=2007-02-13 |accessdate=2010-09-12 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170822134607/http://www.peterdavid.net/archives/005169.html |archivedate=2017-08-22 |deadurl=no }}</ref>，而最後一集則於6月出版<ref name="Stephenking.com/Gunslinger Born #7">{{cite web |url=http://stephenking.com/darktower/comic/the_dark_tower_the_gunslinger_born_7.html |title=The Dark Tower: The Gunslinger Born #7 |publisher=Stephenking.com |accessdate=2017-08-18 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170822095856/http://stephenking.com/darktower/comic/the_dark_tower_the_gunslinger_born_7.html |archivedate=2017-08-22 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。接著，其他幾套漫畫書也陸陸續續出版。

