{{Main article|黑塔 (電影)}}

將《黑塔》小說改編成電影的作業由[[J·J·亞伯拉罕|J·J·亞伯拉罕]]於2007年起頭<ref>{{cite web |url=http://au.movies.ign.com/articles/764/764210p1.html |title=Who is Lost in The Dark Tower? |publisher=''[[IGN|IGN]]'' |date=2007-02-13 |accessdate=2007-02-14 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160306133811/http://www.ign.com/articles/2007/02/13/who-is-lost-in-the-dark-tower |archivedate=2016-03-06 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>，但他於2009年10月表示，自己已不再參與該計劃<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.mtv.com/news/2434355/jj-abrams-will-not-be-building-his-dark-tower/ |title=J.J. Abrams Will Not Be Building His 'Dark Tower' |publisher=MTV |last=Ditzian |first=Eric |date=2009-10-11 |accessdate=2017-06-07 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170602165221/http://www.mtv.com/news/2434355/jj-abrams-will-not-be-building-his-dark-tower/ |archivedate=2017-06-02 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。2010年10月29日，據報導，《黑塔》電影三部曲中的首部電影將於2013年5月17日由[[環球影業|環球影業]]發行<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.comingsoon.net/news/movienews.php?id=71268 |title=Universal Sets Release Dates Through 2013 |publisher=ComingSoon.net |date=2010-10-29 |accessdate=2012-01-09 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160522081111/http://www.comingsoon.net/movies/news/71268-universal-sets-release-dates-through-2013 |archivedate=2016-05-22 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。2011年7月19日，[[環球影業|環球影業]]取消了對《黑塔》電影及電視劇製作的支持。據報導，工作室無法與製片人[[朗·霍華|朗·霍華]]達成協議<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.empireonline.com/news/story.asp?NID=31502 |title=Universal Dismantles The Dark Tower | Movie News | Empire |publisher=''[[帝國雜誌|Empire]]'' |last=White |first=James |date=2011-07-19 |accessdate=2012-01-09 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160619124041/http://www.empireonline.com/movies/news/universal-dismantles-dark-tower/ |archivedate=2016-06-19 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。儘管如此，製作人[[白賴仁·基沙|白賴仁·基沙]]證實，改編作業仍會持續進行，並指出[[HBO|HBO]]已開始製作改編自《黑塔》系列小說的電視劇<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.mtv.com/news/2440221/dark-tower-hbo-brian-grazer/ |title='Dark Tower' Heading To HBO, Says Brian Grazer |publisher=MTV |last=Wigler |first=Josh |date=2011-10-25 |accessdate=2012-01-09 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161222121831/http://www.mtv.com/news/2440221/dark-tower-hbo-brian-grazer// |archivedate=2016-12-22 |deadurl=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |last=Blauvelt |first=Christian |url=https://ew.com/article/2011/07/19/stephen-king-dark-tower-universal/ |title=Stephen King 'Dark Tower' |publisher=''[[娱乐周刊|Entertainment Weekly]]'' |date=2011-07-19 |accessdate=2012-01-09 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160816013143/http://www.ew.com/article/2011/07/19/stephen-king-dark-tower-universal |archivedate=2016-08-16 |deadurl=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/live-feed/brian-grazer-stephen-kings-dark-tower-still-a-go-at-hbo-253110 |title=Brian Grazer: Stephen King's 'The Dark Tower' Still a Go at HBO |publisher=''[[荷里活報道|The Hollywood Reporter]]'' |date=2011-10-25 |accessdate=2020-01-24 }}</ref>。2012年3月13日，據報導，[[華納兄弟|華納兄弟]]表示，他們有興趣製作第一部《黑塔》電影，而曾打算飾演[[羅蘭·德斯欽|羅蘭·德斯欽]]的[[羅素·克洛|羅素·克洛]]則退出了劇組。該報導指出，拍攝作業可能會在2013年開始<ref>{{cite web |last=Child |first=Ben |url=https://www.theguardian.com/film/2012/mar/13/dark-tower-film-warner-bros |title=The Dark Tower film project picked up by Warner Bros. |publisher=''[[衛報|The Guardian]]'' |date=2012-03-13 |accessdate=2012-03-13 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160315095348/http://www.theguardian.com/film/2012/mar/13/dark-tower-film-warner-bros |archivedate=2016-03-15 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。然而，華納兄弟最終選擇將電影轉手交給其他工作室製作<ref name="WB">{{cite web |url=http://www.slashfilm.com/warner-bros-passes-on-ron-howards-adaptation-of-stephen-kings-the-dark-tower/#more-134797 |title=Warner Bros. Passes on Ron Howard's Adaptation of Stephen King's 'The Dark Tower' |work={{link-en|/Film|/Film}} |last=Fischer |first=Russ |date=2012-08-20 |accessdate=2017-06-08 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160309214313/http://www.slashfilm.com/warner-bros-passes-on-ron-howards-adaptation-of-stephen-kings-the-dark-tower/#more-134797 |archivedate=2016-03-09 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。

