/web/20171005050637/http://www.ew.com/article/2016/02/29/dark-tower-rises-stephen-king-idris-elba-and-matthew-mcconaughey |archivedate=2017-10-05 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。據3月5日的報導指出，美國的發行日期推遲至2017年2月13日<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.comingsoon.net/movies/news/663479-sony-shifts-release-dates-for-the-dark-tower-bad-boys-3-and-barbie#/slide/1 |title=Sony Moves Release Date for Bad Boys 3 and More |work=ComingSoon.net |date=2016-03-05 |accessdate=2017-06-06 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161028022743/http://www.comingsoon.net/movies/news/663479-sony-shifts-release-dates-for-the-dark-tower-bad-boys-3-and-barbie#/slide/1 |archivedate=2016-10-28 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。電影於2016年4月在[[南非|南非]]開拍<ref>{{cite news |last1=Pesce |first1=Nicole Lyn |title=‘The Dark Tower’: First look at Idris Elba as the Gunslinger |url=http://www.nydailynews.com/entertainment/movies/dark-tower-idris-elba-gunslinger-article-1.2639947 |accessdate=2016-06-28 |work=''[[紐約每日新聞|New York Daily News]]'' |date=2016-05-17 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170801234502/http://www.nydailynews.com/entertainment/movies/dark-tower-idris-elba-gunslinger-article-1.2639947 |archivedate=2017-08-01 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。片中也有部分場景在[[紐約|紐約]]取景<ref>{{cite news |title=Man in black! Matthew McConaughey dyes hair darker for his role |url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-3668873/Man-black-Matthew-McConaughey-gets-character-shows-freshly-dyed-hair-set-Dark-Tower.html |accessdate=2016-07-01 |work=''[[每日郵報|Daily Mail]]'' |date=2016-06-30 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20160715064827/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-3668873/Man-black-Matthew-McConaughey-gets-character-shows-freshly-dyed-hair-set-Dark-Tower.html |archivedate=2016-07-15 }}</ref>。2017年5月3日，首支官方預告片釋出<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.theverge.com/2017/5/3/14973518/the-dark-tower-movie-trailer-stephen-king-watch |title=The first trailer for Stephen King’s The Dark Tower is here |date=2017-05-03 |work=''[[The_Verge|The Verge]]'' |accessdate=2017-05-03 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170805060941/https://www.theverge.com/2017/5/3/14973518/the-dark-tower-movie-trailer-stephen-king-watch |archivedate=2017-08-05 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。電影最終於2017年8月4日上映<ref>{{cite web |work=IMDb |title=The Dark Tower (2017) Release Info |url=http://www.imdb.com/title/tt1648190/releaseinfo?ref_=tt_dt_dt |accessdate=2017-06-11 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20171018201751/http://www.imdb.com/title/tt1648190/releaseinfo?ref_=tt_dt_dt |archivedate=2017-10-18 |deadurl=no }}</ref>，所獲評價以負面居多<ref>{{cite web |title=The Dark Tower (2017) |url=https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_dark_tower_2017 |website=Rotten Tomatoes |publisher=Fandango |accessdate=2017-08-04 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170915215952/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_dark_tower_2017 |archivedate=2017-09-15 |deadurl=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=The Dark Tower reviews |url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/the-dark-tower |work=Metacritic |publisher=CBS Interactive |accessdate=2017-08-04 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170828215332/http://www.metacritic.com/movie/the-dark-tower |archivedate=2017-08-28 |deadurl=no }}</ref><ref name="TheWrap">{{cite web |last=Callahan |first=Dan |url=http://www.thewrap.com/dark-tower-review-big-screen-adaptation-stephen-kings-gunslinger-epic-misfires/ |title='The Dark Tower’ Review: Big Screen Adaptation of Stephen King’s Gunslinger Epic Misfires |work=''[[TheWrap|TheWrap]]'' |date=2017-08-02 |accessdate=2017-08-04 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170826074134/http://www.thewrap.com/dark-tower-review-big-screen-adaptation-stephen-kings-gunslinger-epic-misfires/ |archivedate=2017-08-26 |deadurl=no }}</ref><ref name="Uproxx">{{cite web |last=Ryan |first=Mike |url=http://uproxx.com/movies/the-dark-tower-review/ |title=‘The Dark Tower’ Review: What The Hell Happened? |website={{link-en|Uproxx|Uproxx}} |date=2017-08-02 |accessdate=2017-08-03 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170926190916/http://uproxx.com/movies/the-dark-tower-review/ |archivedate=2017-09-26 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>，有影評人認為該片的劇情既脫離原著又糟糕<ref name="Uproxx"/><ref>{{cite web |last=Loughrey |first=Clarisse |url=http://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/films/news/the-dark-tower-reviews-critics-release-date-trailer-stephen-king-adaptation-idris-elba-matthew-a7874286.html |title=The Dark Tower review round-up: Stephen King adaptation disappoints both newbies and fans |work=''[[The_Independent|The Independent]]'' |date=2017-08-03 |accessdate=2017-08-10 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20171014234041/http://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/films/news/the-dark-tower-reviews-critics-release-date-trailer-stephen-king-adaptation-idris-elba-matthew-a7874286.html |archivedate=2017-10-14 |deadurl=no }}</ref>，但艾巴飾演羅蘭的表現獲得了影評青睞<ref>{{cite web|url=https://hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/dark-tower-idris-elba-is-good-movie-1026991|title=Idris Elba Is Too Good for 'The Dark Tower'|work=''[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]]''|last=Spiegel|first=Josh|date=2017-08-05|accessdate=2017-08-27|archive-date=2017-08-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170805211218/https://hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/dark-tower-idris-elba-is-good-movie-1026991|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.aintitcool.com/node/78298|title=Quint thinks the Dark Tower movie is monotone, flat and a massive wasted opportunity|publisher={{link-en|Ain't It Cool News|Ain't It Cool News}}|last=Vespe|first=Eric|date=2017-08-03|accessdate=2017-08-03|archive-date=2017-08-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170803173533/http://www.aintitcool.com/node/78298|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |last=Mendelson |first=Scott |url=https://www.forbes.com/sites/scottmendelson/2017/08/04/why-idris-elba-makes-the-dark-tower-a-must-see-in-theaters/#3aa279f5283e/ |title=Why Idris Elba Makes 'The Dark Tower' A Must-See In Theaters |work=''[[福布斯|Forbes]]'' |date=2017-08-0