==== 衍生電視劇 ====

2016年9月，《[[娛樂周刊|娛樂周刊]]》報導，待電影上映後，與電影相同世界觀的《黑塔》電視劇將於2018年推出，由{{link-en|媒體權利資本公司|Media Rights Capital}}（MRC）製作，{{link-en|葛倫·馬札拉|Glen Mazzara}}擔任[[節目統籌|節目統籌]]，演員[[伊卓瑞斯·艾巴|伊卓瑞斯·艾巴]]（飾演[[羅蘭·德斯欽|羅蘭·德斯欽]]）、{{link-en|湯姆·泰勒 (演員)|Tom Taylor (actor)|湯姆·泰勒}}（飾演傑克·錢伯斯）與[[丹尼斯·赫柏特|丹尼斯·赫柏特]]（飾演史蒂芬·德斯欽）都將回歸出演。據報導，該劇會補充電影的背景故事，且會有新演員來飾演年輕時的羅蘭及[[華特·派帝克|華特·派帝克]]。該劇的劇情改編自《[[黑塔IV_巫師與水晶球|黑塔IV 巫師與水晶球]]》及外傳《[[穿過鑰匙孔的風|穿過鑰匙孔的風]]》，同時也會帶有《[[黑塔I_最後的槍客|黑塔I 最後的槍客]]》的元素。<ref>{{cite web |last=Breznican |first=Anthony |url=http://www.ew.com/article/2016/09/21/dark-tower-tv-series-stephen-king-wizard-glass |title='The Dark Tower' TV Series Will Adapt Stephen King's 'Wizard and Glass' |publisher=''[[娱乐周刊|Entertainment Weekly]]'' |date=2016-09-21 |accessdate=2017-08-06 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160922153401/http://www.ew.com/article/2016/09/21/dark-tower-tv-series-stephen-king-wizard-glass |archivedate=2016-09-22 |deadurl=no }}</ref>馬札拉表示，該電視劇將會探討「為何華特會成為黑衣人，以及他與羅蘭之間的讓羅蘭失去一切及所愛之人的競爭」<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.empireonline.com/people/stephen-king/walking-dead-veteran-glen-mazzara-run-dark-tower-tv-series/ |title=Walking Dead Veteran Glen Mazzara To Run The Dark Tower TV Series |publisher=''[[帝國雜誌|Empire]]'' |last=White |first=James |date=2017-08-03 |accessdate=2017-08-09 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170809175217/http://www.empireonline.com/people/stephen-king/walking-dead-veteran-glen-mazzara-run-dark-tower-tv-series/ |archivedate=2017-08-09 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。2018年2月，據報導，[[亞馬遜公司|亞馬遜公司]]買下了《黑塔》的電視劇改編權，但亞馬遜公司並未證實這一點。此外，艾巴、泰勒和赫柏特是否回歸成了未知數<ref>{{cite web |last1=Saavedra |first1=John |title=The Dark Tower TV Series Is Coming to Amazon |url=http://www.denofgeek.com/us/tv/the-dark-tower/258624/the-dark-tower-tv-series-is-coming-to-amazon |work=Den of Geek |date=2018-02-25 |accessdate=2018-03-09 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6xmgwmPsw?url=http://www.denofgeek.com/us/tv/the-dark-tower/258624/the-dark-tower-tv-series-is-coming-to-amazon |archivedate=2018-03-09 |deadurl=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |last1=Colburn |first1=Randall |title=The Dark Tower TV Series Is Coming to Amazon |url=https://consequenceofsound.net/2018/02/a-tv-adaptation-of-stephen-kings-the-dark-tower-is-happening-at-amazon-report/ |work=''[[前音後果|Consequence of Sound]]'' |date=2018-02-25 |accessdate=2018-07-02 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180613141133/https://consequenceofsound.net/2018/02/a-tv-adaptation-of-stephen-kings-the-dark-tower-is-happening-at-amazon-report/ |archivedate=2018-06-13 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |last1=Evangelista |first1=Chris |title=‘The Dark Tower’ TV Series ‘Very Much Alive’ at Amazon – Here’s How to Not Screw It Up |url=http://www.slashfilm.com/dark-tower-tv-series-amazon/ |work={{link-en|/Film|/Film}} |date=2018-06-12 |accessdate=2018-07-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180702175809/http://www.slashfilm.com/dark-tower-tv-series-amazon/ |archive-date=2018-07-02 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |last1=Feldberg |first1=Isaac |title=The Dark Tower TV series somehow still 'alive' at Amazon |url=http://ew.com/tv/2018/06/12/the-dark-tower-tv-series-somehow-still-alive-at-amazon/ |work=''Entertainment Weekly'' |date=2018-06-12 |accessdate=2018-07-02 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180615000823/http://ew.com/tv/2018/06/12/the-dark-tower-tv-series-somehow-still-alive-at-amazon/ |archivedate=2018-06-15 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |last1=Fitzpatrick |first1=Kevin |title=HAS ‘THE DARK TOWER’ TV SERIES LANDED AT AMAZON? |url=http://screencrush.com/dark-tower-tv-series-amazon/ |work=''ScreenCrush'' |date=2018-06-12 |accessdate=2018-07-02 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180524230529/http://screencrush.com/dark-tower-tv-series-amazon/ |archivedate=2018-05-24 }}</ref>。3月，根據《[[綜藝_(雜誌)|綜藝]]》雜誌報導，該劇將講述羅蘭成為槍客的起源，以及他與華特的第一次交手，而亞馬遜公司已承諾製作兩季。該劇的主演也重新選過，據消息人士透露，[[電視試播|試播集]]中的羅蘭和華特將分別由英國男演員{{link-en|山姆·史崔克|Sam Strike}}和芬蘭男演員[[亚斯佩尔·派科宁|亚斯佩尔·派科宁]]飾演<ref>{{cite web|last=Otterson|first=Joe|url=https://variety.com/2019/tv/news/dark-tower-series-amazon-jasper-paakkonen-sam-strike-1203169085/|title=‘Dark Tower’ Pilot at Amazon Casts Jasper Pääkkönen, Sam Strike|work=''Variety''|date=2019-03-21|accessdate=2019-03-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190321174935/https://variety.com/2019/tv/news/dark-tower-series-amazon-jasper-paakkonen-sam-strike-1203169085/|archive-date=2019-03-21|dead-url=no}}</ref>。電視劇於6月正式開拍，與此同時[[迈克尔·鲁克|迈克尔·鲁克]]、{{link-en|傑羅姆·弗林|Jerome Flynn}}和喬安納·里貝羅（{{lang|en|Joana Ribeiro}}）也加入了演員陣容<ref>{{cite web|last=Andreeva|first=Nellie|url=https://deadline.com/2019/06/the-dark-tower-michael-rooker-cast-amazon-pilot-1202631117/|title=‘The Dark Tower’: Michael Rooker Co-Stars In Amazon Pilot|work=Deadline.com|date=2019-06-11|accessdate=2019-06-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190611224735/https://deadline.com/2019/06/the-dark-tower-michael-rooker-cast-amazon-pilot-1202631117/|archive-date=2019-06-11|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2020年1月，亞馬遜公司宣布，他們不會再推動試播集的進度，不過製作公司MRC已經在物色其他劇本<ref>{{cite web |last1=Andreeva |first1=Nellie |title=‘The Dark Tower’ Series Adaptation Not Going Forward At Amazon |url=https://deadline.com/2020/01/the-dark-tower-series-adaptation-dead-pilot-amazon-not-going-forward-1202830606/ |website=''[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]]'' |date=2020-01-15 |accessdate=2020-01-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200116014348/https://deadline.com/2020/01/the-dark-tower-series-adaptation-dead-pilot-amazon-not-going-forward-1202830606/ |archive-date=2020-01-16 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==== 續集 ====

[[史蒂芬·金|史蒂芬·金]]在受訪時表示，自己希望能參與《[[黑塔_(電影)|黑塔]]》續集的製作，並透露續集將是一部[[美国电影分级制度#美國電影協會電影分級|R級]]電影{{refnest|group="附註"|[[美国电影分级制度|美國電影分級制度]]中，R級是「未滿17歲（的觀眾）必須由家長或成年監護人陪同才能入場觀看」的電影<ref>{{cite web |title=Film Ratings |publisher=[[美國電影協會|Motion Picture Association of America]] |url=http://www.mpaa.org/film-ratings/ |accessdate=2014-03-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140325082704/http://www.mpaa.org/film-ratings/ |archive-date=2014-03-25 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。}}。金還表示，續集中的羅蘭會帶著一頂帽子。<ref>{{cite web |last=Foutch |first=Haleigh |url=http://collider.com/stephen-king-interview-the-dark-tower/ |title=Stephen King Talks ‘The Dark Tower’, Casting Controversy, and Getting Blocked by Trump on Twitter |publisher=[[Collider_(網站)|Collider]] |date=2017-08-03 |accessdate=2017-08-06 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170921081156/http://collider.com/stephen-king-interview-the-dark-tower/ |archivedate=2017-09-21 |deadurl=no }}</ref>《黑塔》的導演[[尼科萊·阿爾賽|尼科萊·阿爾賽]]在受訪時宣布，續集將根據《[[黑塔II_三張預言牌|黑塔II 三張預言牌]]》改編，艾迪與蘇珊娜將會登場<ref>{{cite web |last=Evry |first=Max |url=http://www.comingsoon.net/movies/features/876489-director-nikolaj-arcel-talks-dark-tower-ending-and-sequels-spoilers#/slide/1 |title=Director Nikolaj Arcel Talks Dark Tower Ending and Sequels (SPOILERS) |publisher=Comingsoon.net |date=2017-08-07 |accessdate=2017-08-13 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20171017172601/http://www.comingsoon.net/movies/features/876489-director-nikolaj-arcel-talks-dark-tower-ending-and-sequels-spoilers#/slide/1 |archivedate=2017-10-17 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。

